OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FMackenzie blames herself. Tane
OL,7,     Fbreaks some devastating news.
OL,8,     FDavid hands Richie a learning
OL,9,     Fopportunity.
OL,10,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,11,     FThis week at the Hall Green Health
OL,12,     FCentre, the doctors work to get to
OL,13,     Fthe bottom of various conditions.
OL,14,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,15,     FDr Julian Humphrey treats one
OL,16,     Fpatient with a aortic dissection,
OL,17,     Fand another with a regularly
OL,18,     Fdislocated shoulder. Documentary
OL,19,     Fseries filmed inside Barnsley
OL,20,     Fcasualty department.
