OL,5,G2100 999: Critical Condition
OL,6,     FHaving plummeted 15 feet onto
OL,7,     Fconcrete, Michael is rushed into
OL,8,     Fresus with a significant
OL,9,     Flaceration to his head. And a
OL,10,     Fdriver has a crushed leg after
OL,11,     Fbeing run over by his own van.
OL,12,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FA patient brought into A&E by
OL,14,     Fpolice claims to have swallowed
OL,15,     Fdrugs, but he refuses to
OL,16,     Fco-operate with staff, putting the
OL,17,     FNHS under further pressure.
