OL,13,     FDr Adil Sheraz removes a giant
OL,14,     Flipoma from a patient's back,
OL,15,     Fwhile Dr Toby Nelson tackles 13
OL,16,     Flipomas on a single patient, and
OL,17,     Fthere's a nasty face cyst for Dr
OL,18,     FEmma McMullen.
